---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | ByteLite LLC"
  description="Privacy policy for the ByteLite LLC website and HeartStrings ecosystem."
  keywords="ByteLite LLC privacy policy"
  
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-sub">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container legal-body">

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>ByteLite LLC is committed to privacy as a design requirement, not a legal checkbox. This policy describes what data is collected through this website and under what conditions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>What this website collects</h2>
        <h3>Contact form submissions</h3>
        <p>If you submit the contact form, your name, email address, and message are collected. This data is used solely to respond to your inquiry. It is not sold, shared with third parties, or used for marketing without your consent.</p>
        <h3>Analytics</h3>
        <p>This website may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand aggregate traffic patterns. If used, analytics are configured to anonymize IP addresses and not track individuals across sites. No advertising profiles are created.</p>
        <h3>Cookies</h3>
        <p>A minimal cookie consent preference may be stored locally to remember your choice. No advertising cookies are set by this website.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>What this website does not do</h2>
        <ul class="legal-list">
          <li>Sell personal information to third parties</li>
          <li>Create advertising profiles</li>
          <li>Track individuals across other websites</li>
          <li>Use behavioral targeting advertising</li>
          <li>Retain contact form data beyond the purpose of responding</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>HeartStrings App</h2>
        <p>HeartStrings App is in private Android test and beta development only. It is not available on any public app store. A separate, app-specific privacy policy will be published before any broader beta release or public app launch. Beta participants are informed of data handling specific to their testing role.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Restaurant promotion pilot</h2>
        <p>The HeartStrings restaurant promotion pilot collects restaurant account details, business profile information, and the promotional deal a participating restaurant chooses to offer. Payments for the pilot are handled by Stripe as the payment processor; ByteLite LLC does not receive or store card data.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>This website may use third-party services for hosting, form handling, or analytics. Such services are selected for their privacy posture. ByteLite LLC does not use advertising networks on this website.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>You may request deletion of any contact form data submitted by emailing through the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>. ByteLite LLC will respond within a reasonable timeframe.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>This policy may be updated as ByteLite LLC's products develop. The updated date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision. Material changes will be noted.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Privacy questions may be directed through the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>. ByteLite LLC is based in Helena, Montana, USA.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>

.legal-hero { padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem; }
.legal-hero h1 { max-width: 480px; }
.legal-sub { margin-top: .75rem; font-size: .9375rem; color: #555e7a; }
.legal-body { max-width: 760px; }
.legal-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.legal-section h2 { font-size: 1.375rem; color: #e4e7f2; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-bottom: .75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2235; }
.legal-section h3 { font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #e4e7f2; margin: 1.5rem 0 .5rem; }
.legal-section p { font-size: .9375rem; color: #7b829e; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: .875rem; }
.legal-section a { color: #818cf8; }
.legal-section a:hover { color: #a5b4fc; }
.legal-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .625rem; }
.legal-list li { font-size: .9375rem; color: #7b829e; padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.6; }
.legal-list li::before { content: "—"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4a5068; }

</style>
